description:
Space Marine 2 features 6 different classes in its PvE Co-Op mode, Operations.
Players can choose from the Tactical marine, Assault, Bulwark, Sniper, Vanguard, and Heavy classes, all with their own arsenal of weapons and unique perks. 

In this gameplay from the preview build of Warhammer 40,000 Space Marine 2 you can see all of the classes in action as they tear apart Tyranids in the name of The Emperor.

00:00 Tactical
03:20 Assault
07:54 Vanguard
11:59 Bulwark
14:55 Heavy
18:01 Sniper
21:24 Hive Tyrant Boss Fight
title: Warhammer 40k: Space Marine 2 - All Classes PvE Co-Op Gameplay
